    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Meat Fest 是一款动态射击游戏，拥有类似灵魂的元素、竞技场和走廊、秘密、陷阱和自己的故事。 建立在优秀的老射手的基础上，加上现代的便利，它提出了社会的社会问题。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>要回答问题，您必须使用各种武器、斧头和套装来保护自己并躲避致命打击和危险动物。一点一点地收集故事，找到真相，真相总是潜伏在附近的某个地方。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><i>阴谋</i></u> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <i>人类被迫离开他们的家园，定居在 Radix，那里的领导人告诉新一代，地球是因自然灾害而毁灭的。战斗遗传学家 Marcus Berger 研究了人类家园的样本，开始意识到这些关于世界灭亡的说法是多么虚假。他越来越沉浸在寻找真相的过程中，并接触了主要由反对派组成的黑市经销商。他的本土公司开始将他视为危险单位，Marcus 逃离了 Radix，决定在地球上寻找答案。玩家必须面对人类摇篮中的现有居民，并找到人为灾难理论的证据，正是这场灾难让世界变成了地狱。</i> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><u>更多</u></i></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结合你的攻击</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056860/extras/e9a9a49e880c0d64e856d6bab27aa350.poster.avif?t=1755033323\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056860/extras/e9a9a49e880c0d64e856d6bab27aa350.webm?t=1755033323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056860/extras/e9a9a49e880c0d64e856d6bab27aa350.mp4?t=1755033323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择你的游戏风格</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056860/extras/c696bc91d0a9560d80238c8d720af1ef.poster.avif?t=1755033323\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056860/extras/c696bc91d0a9560d80238c8d720af1ef.webm?t=1755033323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056860/extras/c696bc91d0a9560d80238c8d720af1ef.mp4?t=1755033323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跳板将帮助你克服天选之子的道路，在战斗中生存或补充补给</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056860/extras/9df004a589affc581d94f532fcdc7f95.poster.avif?t=1755033323\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056860/extras/9df004a589affc581d94f532fcdc7f95.webm?t=1755033323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056860/extras/9df004a589affc581d94f532fcdc7f95.mp4?t=1755033323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >找到所有的秘密。奖励等待那些特别的人细心</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056860/extras/b90d3f08a4197d01aeae360a03e926c1.poster.avif?t=1755033323\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056860/extras/b90d3f08a4197d01aeae360a03e926c1.webm?t=1755033323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056860/extras/b90d3f08a4197d01aeae360a03e926c1.mp4?t=1755033323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p>",
